The paper deals with the security of zero-interaction authentication systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of multiple sensors and devices to capture a user's walking pattern, which could be classified under human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computer vision (cs.CV), multimedia (cs.MM), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
